        " \"يُصَلَّى عَلَى اَلَّذِي فِيهِ قَلْبُهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5378 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) was asked about a man who was killed and whose body parts were found scattered.\nHow should the funeral prayer be performed for him?\nImam (as) said: \"The prayer should be performed over the part that contains his heart.\""
        ]
      }
